{"tid":142174,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"如何抗衡仆街同事","createTime":"2017-03-03T13:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T15:10:04.000Z","uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d83f005ba258dbf3a6103f4576ae89799026ecd4","tid":142174,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:56:25.000Z","msg":"半年前黎左個仆街女同事<br />\n開頭幾nice 又好有笑容<br />\n點知之後就見真章<br />\n<br />\n有時好心 見佢教個活動就仆街<br />\n直接 婉轉 間接講哂方法俾佢聽<br />\n佢依然覺得人地會線鳩佢咁<br />\n仲要張所有責任推哂佢人地到<br />\n<br />\n我一放假 就馬上向老細督背瘠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女人真係CLS 20幾歲 <br />\n份工大家都覺得係踏腳石 間公司無咩前途可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都要踏底人 抬高自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd3a69326f79536f75c09fea3f9aa19b0455ccd","tid":142174,"uid":33033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T14:00:33.000Z","msg":"溝左佢"},{"pid":"af5f1591af489aaaa097ff0ce5902c5bcab0c464","tid":142174,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:08:36.000Z","msg":"仆街過佢"},{"pid":"b7d40ca2ef8fa61ffe2b233a69d10e2e74d8e2dd","tid":142174,"uid":13879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"俾盡幾多？"}]}